OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Households in England, Scotland and    
OL,6, Wales are set to have hundreds of      
OL,7, pounds knocked off energy bills as part
OL,8, of a package worth billions to help    
OL,9, people cope with soaring prices.       
OL,11,FThe government is to scrap a plan to   
OL,12,Fgive people #200 off bills from October
OL,13,Fwhich would be repaid over five years. 
OL,15,FInstead, the BBC understands that sum  
OL,16,Fwill be increased and possibly doubled,
OL,17,Fand will not need to be paid back.     
OL,19,FAdditional help for those on the lowest
OL,20,Fincomes is also expected.              
